casebody.data: In the MATTER OF DISCIPLINE OF Philip R. FARTHING. No. D-3065 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020 Philip R. Farthing, of Norfolk, Virginia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
